The <!DOCTYPE> declaration represents the document type, and helps browsers to display webpages correctly.
The <html> element defines the whole document.
Inside the <html> element is the <body> element.The body element defines the document body.
We can put elements inside other elements too called nesting.
The <center> tag was used to center-align text in HTML document.
padding-left, padding-top and other alignments were used to align text in the HTML document.
